OL,5, The government is being taken to court 
OL,6, today by 276 deaf people over the lack 
OL,7, of British Sign Language (BSL)         
OL,8, interpretation at the televised        
OL,9, coronavirus briefings.                 
OL,11,FThe hearing at the Royal Courts of     
OL,12,FJustice in London will see a judge     
OL,13,Fdecide if the complainants are entitled
OL,14,Fto compensation.                       
OL,16,FCampaigner Lynn Stewart-Taylor says the
OL,17,Flack of provision during the pandemic  
OL,18,Fmade the deaf community feel "excluded"
OL,19,Fand "like we're an afterthought."      
